description: Numbers whose 4th power can be expressed as the sum of two positive cubes in more than one way.
links: Chai Wah Wu, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..358
prog: (PARI) for(i=1, 10^5, x=i^4; c=0; for(j=1, floor(sqrtn(x/2,3)), if(ispower(x-j^3,3), c++)); if(c>1, print(i" "c))) [From _Donovan Johnson_, Aug 03 2009]
author: _Jud McCranie_
extensions: More terms from _John W. Layman_, Feb 24 2003
